{"title":"调教Hexo之个性化","slug":"调教Hexo之个性化","date":"2018-03-16T10:56:41.000Z","updated":"2018-03-16T17:16:40.305Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/调教Hexo之个性化.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"本来想自己的hexo搞得个性化一点，然而难受的是，一搜索hexo个性化，全是next主题的各种骚操作，但是看看我们的主题，简直日了狗好吧。<br>没办法，不想用那种烂大街的东西，就只好自己多找点插件用用了，不是前端工程师的悲哀。。。。","covers":["http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/layout.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/atom-dark.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/base16-ateliersulphurpool.light","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/ghcolors.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/okaidia.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png","http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/twilight.png"],"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>本来想自己的hexo搞得个性化一点，然而难受的是，一搜索hexo个性化，全是next主题的各种骚操作，但是看看我们的主题，简直日了狗好吧。<br>没办法，不想用那种烂大街的东西，就只好自己多找点插件用用了，不是前端工程师的悲哀。。。。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p><em>我的主题为<a href=\"https://github.com/HeskeyBaozi/hexo-theme-lite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lite</a>，以下配置均依照该主题设置，但是我说的方法都是通用的</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"七牛图床同步插件\"><a href=\"#七牛图床同步插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七牛图床同步插件\"></a>七牛图床同步插件</h2><p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/gyk001/hexo-qiniu-sync\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">该插件</a>之后，可以直接将图片放到本地，然后通过 </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">{% qnimg imageFile %} \n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>直接引用</p>\n<h2 id=\"站点收录\"><a href=\"#站点收录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"站点收录\"></a>站点收录</h2><h3 id=\"本地配置\"><a href=\"#本地配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地配置\"></a>本地配置</h3><p>在根目录下运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap --save\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hexo-generator-sitemap --save\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后在根目录的配置文件下添加</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\"># 自动生成sitemap</span>\nsitemap:\n  path: sitemap.xml\nbaidusitemap:\n  path: baidusitemap.xml\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>还有记得修改url为自己的域名<br>重新生成后就可以在public目录里面看到sitemap.xml和baidusitemap.xml文件了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"引擎收录\"><a href=\"#引擎收录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引擎收录\"></a>引擎收录</h3><blockquote>\n<p>很不幸的告诉你，上面配置的百度站点地图完全是白费的23333<br>因为github阻止了百度的爬虫，所以你在百度站长平台认证时，通不过的。<br>如果你死都想让百度收录。。。。骚年，我浪费了我整整1天来告诉你——–死了这条心吧<br>网上的答案不外乎：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>不使用github的pages，转而使用其他的替代pages。然而国内的coding：对个人博客会有5秒跳转，除非你在你的博客中加入coding的标识（mmp，乘火打劫，而且图标还丑的一批，而且这个跳转机制有时还会让爬虫失效。）。码云：不支持自定义域名。国外的gitlab：日您！还需要用CI/CD在服务器部署，我弄了大半天都没弄出来！</li>\n<li>使用域名服务器进行海外海内分别解析。比如把国内解析到coding上，国外的解析到github上。但是cloudflare说：臣妾做不到啊！如果你想换用国内的域名服务器，那么https手动和您再见。如果你想自己用免费的ssl证书，那么请使用自己的vps（不就是钱吗，微笑）。我曾经用过do做自己的hexo服务器，但是这又是一个大坑啊啊啊啊啊，我第一次配置也花了1天多啊。我现在还是回到了github，就是省心，老年人玩不动了。。。。。。</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>不过安慰自己的就是，现在开发人员谁不是用google。恩，所以我们来看看谷歌收录吧。<br>首先登录google站长<a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/#?modal_active=none，然后`添加属性`，输入域名。\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.google.com/webmasters/#?modal_active=none，然后`添加属性`，输入域名。</a><br>验证方法有多种。如果使用文件验证，请把文件放到你的主题目录文件下的source文件夹中，这样生成的时候会一起生成。<br>但是我使用的主题，url后面都会带一个/#,所以验证文件的url和google期望的不一样，于是我使用的是标签验证。找到主题目录下的layout目录，我的里面只有一个文件，然后修改文件，加入标签即可。<br>最后在抓取中找到<code>站点地图</code>添加即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"添加点击效果\"><a href=\"#添加点击效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加点击效果\"></a>添加点击效果</h2><ol>\n<li>确定主题的js文件所在。可以找到\\themes\\lite\\layout目录下的文件，我的是index.ejs，打开后查看已有的js路径<img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/layout.png\">\n比如这里有<code>&lt;script type=text/javascript src=/static/js/manifest.9c14e4c25ff8a4ffed18.js&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>这样的代码，然后我在<code>\\themes\\lite\\source\\static\\js</code>下找到了该js文件。每个主题的js存放目录都不一样，需要自己去找。</li>\n<li>将<a href=\"https://github.com/Neveryu/Neveryu.github.io/blob/master/js/src/love.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">love.js</a>添加到js存放目录，如<code>\\themes\\lite\\source\\static\\js</code></li>\n<li>修改\\themes\\lite\\layout目录下的文件，如index.ejs，在<code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> 标签之前添加如下代码（上方我给出的图片中我已经添加了）<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span> 页面点击小红心 <span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text/javascript\"</span> src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/js/src/love.js\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>重新部署，然后就能看到啦！！！</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"添加2d人物模型\"><a href=\"#添加2d人物模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加2d人物模型\"></a>添加2d人物模型</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">项目地址</a><br>这个文档有中文，安着步骤来一下就成功了，不多说了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"鼠标经过时头像旋转\"><a href=\"#鼠标经过时头像旋转\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"鼠标经过时头像旋转\"></a>鼠标经过时头像旋转</h2><p>打开你的网页，然后右键检查元素，找到头像所在的js文件<br>看到右边样式一栏，点击js文件或者鼠标停在上面就可以看到js文件，然后本地搜索js文件，打开，添加如下代码。代码来自<a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924#articleHeader7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">这里</a>（都是针对的Next主题，很无奈，然后对前端也不熟悉，摸索半天才找出几个能行的）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token class\">.avatar</span><span class=\"token attribute\">[data-v-73f77182]</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4.3</span>rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4.3</span>rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">50%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>px <span class=\"token number\">1</span>px <span class=\"token number\">3</span>px <span class=\"token hexcode\">#fff</span>\n <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 以上为原文件内容 */</span>\n\n <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 设置循环动画 [animation: (play)动画名称 (2s)动画播放时长单位秒或微秒 (ase-out)动画播放的速度曲线为以低速结束 \n    (1s)等待1秒然后开始动画 (1)动画播放次数(infinite为循环播放)] */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过头像旋转360度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 可以自己调这里的时间参数，改变旋转速度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -webkit-transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -moz-transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">img<span class=\"token pseudo-class\">:hover</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过停止头像旋转 \n  -webkit-animation-play-state:paused;\n  animation-play-state:paused; */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过头像旋转360度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* Z 轴旋转动画 */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-webkit-keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-moz-keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"代码高亮\"><a href=\"#代码高亮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码高亮\"></a>代码高亮</h2><p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/ele828/hexo-prism-plugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">这个插件</a><br>有20多种代码样式，够你爽（滑稽<br>我这里试了几种，给你们放个图<br>atom-dark<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/atom-dark.png\"></p>\n<p>base16-ateliersulphurpool.light<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/base16-ateliersulphurpool.light\"></p>\n<p>ghcolors<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/ghcolors.png\"></p>\n<p>okaidia<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/okaidia.png\"></p>\n<p>solarizedlight<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png\"></p>\n<p>tomorrow<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png\"></p>\n<p>twilight<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/twilight.png\"></p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"http://shenzekun.cn/hexo%E7%9A%84next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo的next主题个性化教程:打造炫酷网站</a><br><a href=\"http://fengdi.org/2017/08/10/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%92%8CGoogle%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo博客提交百度和Google收录</a></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}